sub_title: Geophysical consultant at SD2I Geophysical Consulting
summary:
Broadly skilled geophysicist with worldwide expertise in land seismic acquisition, survey evaluation & design, data processing, reservoir geophysics and inversion. Significant involvement in introducing new geophysical technology in Schlumberger and startups. 

Experienced in managing integrated seismic projects.
